{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce1-071-072-he-s-awful",
    "title": "Lesson 71: He's awful!",
    "audioFilename": "071&072－He's Awful.mp3",
    "duration": 122.828,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.43,
      "end": 2.17,
      "text": "Lesson 71.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第71课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 3.11,
      "end": 4.39,
      "text": "He's Awful.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他讨厌透了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 6.09,
      "end": 10.29,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 11.87,
      "end": 16.85,
      "text": "How did Pauline answer the telephone at nine o'clock?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "九点钟时，波琳是怎样接电话的？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 19.63,
      "end": 22.87,
      "text": "What's Ron Marston like, Pauline?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "波琳，罗恩·马斯顿这个人怎么样？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 24.03,
      "end": 25.49,
      "text": "He's awful!",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他讨厌透了！"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 26.51,
      "end": 35.39,
      "text": "He telephoned me four times yesterday, and three times the day before yesterday.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他昨天给我打了四次电话，前天打了三次。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 37.09,
      "end": 44.45,
      "text": "He telephoned the office yesterday morning and yesterday afternoon.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他昨天上午和下午都给办公室打了电话。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 45.55,
      "end": 48.37,
      "text": "My boss answered the telephone.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我的老板接了电话。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 50.07,
      "end": 52.53,
      "text": "What did your boss say to him?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你的老板对他说了什么？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 53.65,
      "end": 57.73,
      "text": "He said, Pauline is typing letters.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他说：“波琳正在打信。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 57.73,
      "end": 60.87,
      "text": "She can't speak to you now.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "她现在不能和你说话。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 62.61,
      "end": 67.89,
      "text": "Then I arrived home at six o'clock yesterday evening.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "后来我昨晚六点钟到家。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 68.85,
      "end": 74.19,
      "text": "He telephoned again, but I didn't answer the phone.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他又打来电话，但我没有接。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 75.61,
      "end": 78.53,
      "text": "Did he telephone again last night?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他昨晚又打电话了吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 79.83,
      "end": 81.41,
      "text": "Yes, he did.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "是的，打了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 82.13,
      "end": 85.11,
      "text": "He telephoned at nine o'clock.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他九点钟打来的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 86.11,
      "end": 88.33,
      "text": "What did you say to him?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你对他说了什么？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 89.63,
      "end": 93.21,
      "text": "I said, this is Pauline's mother.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我说：“我是波琳的母亲。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 93.95,
      "end": 97.79,
      "text": "Please don't telephone my daughter again.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "请别再给我女儿打电话了。”"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 99.49,
      "end": 101.23,
      "text": "Did he telephone again?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "他后来又打了吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 102.13,
      "end": 104.59,
      "text": "No, he didn't.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "不，没有。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
